<br>
See the above link for the dagger I'm taking about is.<br>
<br>
As far as why +BS% items work is because BS caps at 225 for rogues, so they still can reach the hard cap of (252/255).<br>
<br>
However, no item can make you go over the hardcap on abilities.  That's why +med items are pretty much worthless for any 50+ caster as they med is already capped by then.<br>
<br>
I'm still curious if +skill items do stack and if they do, how do they stack.  <br>
<br>
